summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 55W, page 138, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Westholme Addition, Lots 19 to 27, incl., Block 7, located on the northwest corner of W. Genesee St. & 30th Ave. So. W., as Multiple Residence Low Density (RM) Zone.
